        <div class="content-section">
            <h2>Rolling 10-Year Return Analysis</h2>
            <p>While the S&P 500 dominates over the full 50-year timeline, analyzing <strong>rolling 10-year periods</strong> reveals periods where gold was the vastly superior asset class. Below is a breakdown of annualized returns across distinct decades.</p>

            <div class="card" style="overflow-x:auto;">
